name: It's Gonna Get Better
description:
The debut album from Yo, Adrian!  Post-hardcore punk rock from upstate New York.

1. sleeping in trees to avoid bears
2. i have no time for jokes, i have no time for waffles.
3. life is a celebration let's live it together
4. it's never wrong to think about bobby brown
5. have you seen the break-up?  it's really not as bad as you think it might be.
6. i wish i had a time machine and a stronger sense of will (but the latter doesn't exist and the former doesn't run in the family)
7. group hugs, no thugs
8. it's time to play the family feud
9. bill brasky (that son of a bitch)
10. take the fall.  act hurt.  get indignant.
